homes.
   11. (9) ``Empty Nest,'' NBC, 18.8, 17.0 million homes.
   12. (17) ``False Witness'' _ ``NBC Monday Night Movies,'' 18.7,
16.9 million homes.
   13. (11) ``Who's the Boss?'', ABC, 18.6, 16.8 million homes.
   14. (22) ``The Lady Forgets'' _ ``CBS Sunday Movie,'' 18.5, 16.7
million homes.
