</TEXT>
<TEXT>
   21. (20) ``Hunter,'' NBC, 16.2.
   22. (19) ``Head of the Class,'' ABC, 15.8.
   23. (23) ``Night Court,'' NBC, 15.4.
   23. (21) ``Doogie Howser, M.D.,'' ABC, 15.4.
   25. (27) ``Jake and The Fatman,'' CBS, 15.3.
   26. (25) ``Knots Landing,'' CBS, 15.0.
   27. (25) ``Murphy Brown,'' CBS, 14.9.
   28. (X) ``World Series,'' Game 4, ABC, 14.7.
   29. (X) ``Single Women'' _ ``CBS Special Movie,'' 14.6.
