employee, was denied bail after prosecutors argued he might try to
kill or intimidate witnesses.
   U.S. Magistrate Elaine Bucklo on Monday ordered 47-year-old Noah
Robinson jailed for trial.
   Robinson is accused of offering $10,000 for the 1986 slaying of
