   Dr. C. Everett Koop, who wore a military-style
uniform as U.S. surgeon general, will don a cowboy hat next month
as co-chairman of the Great American Smokeout, the American Cancer
Society announced Tuesday.
   Koop's hat will be a twin of the one worn by Larry Hagman, the
